headline: Leidos receives three DISA awards to launch the next phase of IT transformation and end user migrations to the modernized DoDNet
summary: Leidos (NYSE: LDOS) received three new awards from the Defense Information Systems Agency (DISA) to begin the next phase of IT transformation and migrate an expanded user base to the Department of Defense Network (DoDNet) under the Defense Enclave Services (DES) program.
